   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>I, Kallikrates, son of Papeeis, a Persian of the epigone, and my wife, Tasokis, daughter of Harmiysis, a Persian, with me as guardian, being mutual sureties for the repayment, have leased and given the guarantee as aforesaid. Patynion, son of Diodoros, wrote for them since they are illiterate.;(2nd hand) I, Ptolemaios, son of Apion, have leased as aforesaid.</ab>
         </div>
